_sText: GG_CMS2 ======= This map is based on the CMS in it's completed form and location. Picture of the CMS! Currently the map type will be Gungame, but as it's a bit big for this gametype, I'm planning on changing it after the contest is over. Edit: Map have been updated with new higher resolution textures, and removal of bugs. Also, if you have the time, I'd like you to revise your assessments due to the changes made on the map. Enjoy!
